data.description: Grab your imagination and tool belt!  This 4 bed, 1 bath, features a large family room with a wood stove ready for fire Fridays! The living room is currently split for a 5th bed, and the partition can be easily removed. Large fenced front and back yard. This would make for an excellent flipper, investment property or some sweat equity. The seller is currently working on some repairs and clean-up now the roommates are out. The seller will have the roof done before closing.
